title: Marienburg - Sold Down the River (glued map)
description:
WFRP 1st Edition, Marienburg - Sold Down the River (glued map)
==============================================================

Format: PDF of scanned pages
Language: English
First Published: 1999
Publisher: Hogshead Publishing

Sourcepack for the city of Marienburg for use with Warhammer Fantasy Roleplay 1st Edition.

This is an existing scan that is a great conversion to PDF. All I have done is glue the separate map page scans into one giant map.
